    "data": [
        {
            "title": "【中環解密】人行馬年紀念鈔「秒殺」 二手索價9.9萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"504\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/VDhCPxHkM1ocWDNaMljoqQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwNDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/1b059af0-f1a7-11f0-bdeb-a3a68ec700ed\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">每逢農曆新年前夕，人民銀行推出的生肖<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:紀念幣;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/紀念幣\">紀念幣</a>皆有價有市。據內地媒體報道，2026年馬年賀歲紀念幣與紀念鈔前晚（13日）10時正式開售，旋即遭買家「秒殺」搶購，不少民眾慨嘆不到一分鐘就被搶光，多次刷新頁面都苦無機會落單。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時，二級市場價格迅速上揚，每枚10元（人民幣．下同）的馬年紀念幣，溢價幾十元至數百元不等；每張20元面額的紀念鈔，甚至以一套9.9萬元天價放售，相當誇張。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報道指出，預約開始後不到一分鐘，工商銀行頁面顯示已由「系統開放」轉為「額度為0」；多間銀行App亦顯示，紀念幣與紀念鈔的預約瞬間售罄。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">今次發行的2026年賀歲10元紀念幣，材質為雙色銅合金，總共發行一億枚，正面為面額與年份，背面以剪紙風格馬形象為主，輔以花燈和螢草圖案，壁面左側刊「丙午」字樣；至於20元的賀歲紀念鈔，發行量一億張，正面為馬造型主景，背面描繪兒童歡慶鑼鼓場景，同時融合傳統裝飾和多民族文字元素。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0%E8%A7%A3%E5%AF%86-%E4%BA%BA%E8%A1%8C%E9%A6%AC%E5%B9%B4%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E9%88%94-%E7%A7%92%E6%AE%BA-%E4%BA%8C%E6%89%8B%E7%B4%A2%E5%83%B99-9%E8%90%AC-184700625.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-15 08:15:42",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "花旗升恒指目標 年底見3萬  港股四日漲3% 兩萬七關得而復失",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"恒指昨日表現虎頭蛇尾，全日升幅縮至151點，飲恨二萬七關。（何澤攝）\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"504\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nNvzQlo4vf4qo5oeWpGvhQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwNDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/d7e6f260-f1a5-11f0-9b6e-f075c4382f92\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">恒指昨日表現虎頭蛇尾，全日升幅縮至151點，飲恨二萬七關。（何澤攝）</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">港股昨一度漲249點，再升破兩萬七關，但受累內地收緊股票孖展比例的消息，恒指升幅大為收窄，全日漲151點（0.56%），收報26999點，連揚4日，累漲850點（3.25%）。港股今年開局以來進賬逾千點，花旗上周調升恒指目標後，最新報告再次上調約7%，料年底升抵三萬關。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">花旗報告指出，「十五五」規劃路線愈來愈清晰，進一步支持香港和內地股市，上周剛調升恒指年底目標，由27500點升至28800點，最新報告再上調7.3%，至30000點，即今年預測市盈率估算為11.9倍，以反映預期今年企業盈利增長10.1%等因素。該行同時把滬深300指數、MSCI中國指數目標上調7.1%，至5300點和99點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>看好H股 薦買科網護理行業</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">相比A股，花旗更看好H股前景，因為美國減息會對離岸股市有較大支持，而H股亦有更多優質企業，維持科技、康健護理、互聯網行業的「增持」評級，另外加入基本材料板塊，同時下調消費至「中性」、汽車至「減持」評級，首選H股股份包括騰訊（0700.HK）、友邦（1299.HK）、紫金礦業（2899.HK）、藍思科技（6613.HK）、康耐特光學（2276.HK）和恒瑞醫藥（1276.HK）【表】。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3f58f47b-c016-368a-b070-00356cb04ad3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sOJRdz70P7rUtwiovT7tyw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTExMTg7Y2Y9d2VicA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/ef468740-f1a5-11f0-bfff-883a99c976de\" width=\"879\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">昨日港股表現虎頭蛇尾，高開123點，報26971點，之後更抽高249點，報27097點，惟滬深北交易所宣布調高融資保證金最低比例至100%，A股升勢大幅收窄，港股同樣受累，更一度倒跌最多68點，低見26780點，全日最終升151點，報26999點。截至今晨12時，恒指夜期報26879點，跌95點，低水120點，ADR港股比例指數報26910點，較港收市低89點。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">國指昨升0.32%，報9315點；科指漲0.66%至5908點。大市全日成交3403億元，北水淨流入28.64億元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>滬深兩市成交3.9萬億續破頂</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿里巴巴（9988.HK）傳即將發布重磅產品，股價炒高5.7%，同系的阿里健康（0241.HK）更飆19%，為表現最佳藍籌，兩股亦分別獲北水淨買入11.34億元和14.58億元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">A股表現上午好、下午差，上調孖展保證金比例的消息令股市急回，上證指數收報4126點，倒跌12點或0.31%，深成指收14248點，升79點或0.56%，兩市成交3.94萬億元人民幣，再創新高。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8A%B1%E6%97%97%E5%8D%87%E6%81%92%E6%8C%87%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99-%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%95%E8%A6%8B3%E8%90%AC-%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E5%9B%9B%E6%97%A5%E6%BC%B23-%E5%85%A9%E8%90%AC%E4%B8%83%E9%97%9C%E5%BE%97%E8%80%8C%E5%BE%A9%E5%A4%B1-184800902.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-15 08:10:54",
