        },
        {
            "title": "【中環解密】范智廉將加入保誠 接任主席",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"【中環解密】范智廉將加入保誠 接任主席\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"667\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/O8yzuQsn5VV1GfXODWAZXg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY2NztjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/f69217c0-f1a6-11f0-bbf7-fa99930eefda\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">【中環解密】范智廉將加入保誠 接任主席</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0%E8%A7%A3%E5%AF%86-%E8%8C%83%E6%99%BA%E5%BB%89%E5%B0%87%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5%E4%BF%9D%E8%AA%A0-%E6%8E%A5%E4%BB%BB%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD-184800545.html",
